Normally when grouped with the MA and i'm the *only* bard on the  raid I'll twist thus....<br>
Warsong of Zek: 65% haste, Some Raw Atk, Some Str, And 27 pt DS non-puretone disc<br>
Pslam of Veeshan: 160 to *all* resists and 21 pt DS w/ only epic and no amp / puretone<br>
Warsong of the Vah Shir: 25% haste past cap<br>
Chorus of Marr: *AE* 21 mana and 38 hp a tick<br>
My blades proc ATK and STR and AC and Haste buffs for me group (hastes dont stack with WoZ but the AC/ATK/STR do /grin)<br>
<br>
So thats a 90% haste (25% past cap) atk buff, MASSIVE save buff and 48 pt DS that stacks with ANYTHING besides other bards. (and the wussy mana thing too)<br>
<br>
If i /disc purtone, it increases the effectivness of my songs almost twofold. Still 90% haste ( 25% past cap <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) and atk buff, but now its 260 to every resist and a *76* pt DS. If i drop chorus of marr for amplification its a *87* pt DS. These are with *out* Instrument mastery and Singing Mastery AA's and no VoS (bard voice focus item)...if my math is right with full AA's and a VoS i would pump a DS of 105 by *myself*. Stack that with MoR, mage DS, shammy potion DS, and i am hearing DS's of around 205ish from friends. <br>
